      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested across two independent laboratories. Samples were drawn from two manufacturing lots and dimensionally inspected by CMM prior to testing; all specimens conformed to design specification. The sample size exceeds the minimum required and provides sufficient statistical power to characterize inter-specimen variability. Achieved level 3 reflects multi-lot, multi-lab sample provenance."
