      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single load configuration: ASTM F1717 static compression-bending at the standard 35 mm offset. No torsion, fatigue, or varied offset conditions were included in this validation activity. This limits the achieved level to 2 against a required level of 3. The shortfall is addressed by the offset rationale in the decision record, which documents the compensating evidence from the multi-laboratory design and the conservative acceptance bounds applied."
